These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, skateboard, taxi, trike, quad-bike
City: boston, miami, berlin, rome, london, marseilles
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
8. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | skateboard    | taxi  | helicopter      | trike    |
| City      | miami  | marseilles | london | boston | rome | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: august, april, may, september, june, february
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, sprite, 7up, mirinda, coffee
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
9. the person who's birthday is in august is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Birthday   | august   | june | april | february | september     | may  |
| Beverage           | sprite | tea    | cola      | coffee  | 7up | mirinda |

