.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: epic, western, zombie, satire, thriller, comedy
6 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, fish, snake, goldfish, horse
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the fish is the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | comedy   | thriller      | western | epic  | zombie   |
| Pet   | fish | horse | hamster | bird   | goldfish | snake |

