.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, oliveros, swisher, chaman, game, alhambra
6 different pets are kept: horse, frog, dog, turtle, lizard, goat
1. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
5. the owner of the goat is the chaman-smoker##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Cigar   | swisher  | chaman | cain      | oliveros  | alhambra | game |
| Pet     | horse | goat  | lizard | dog | turtle  | frog    |

