.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
6 different games are played: canasta, snooker, monopoly, chess, domino, backgammon
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: snowboarding, biathlon, sailing, cycling, basketball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
10. the person playing chess is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Game         | chess | backgammon | canasta | domino | snooker | monopoly  |
| Sport   | water-polo  | cycling  | sailing  | snowboarding | basketball      | biathlon |

