.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: begonia, zinnia, azalea, sunflower, balloon-flower, aconite
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, roller, tram, bike, van, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person driving the van is the person who growsaconite##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
7. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
9. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Flower   | aconite    | azalea    | begonia | balloon-flower     | zinnia   | sunflower     |
| Transport   | van | roller | skateboard | tram | bike | car |

