.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: techno, indie, trance, soul, funk, ambient
There are 6 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine, dutch, chinese, turkish, italian
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the turkish is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left of the nigerian##1
4. the fan of soul is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the fan of soul is the italian##1
6. the fan of trance is the dutch##1
7. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
8. the fan of indie is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre         | indie       | ambient     | soul | trance | funk | techno |
| Nationality   | argentine | turkish | italian | dutch     | nigerian  | chinese       |

