.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: time-travel, mystery, action, documentary, horror, adventure
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, september, october, june, december, january
1. the person watching action movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person watching adventure movies##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel  | horror     | action    | mystery  | documentary          |
| Birthday         | september  | april | october | december | june | january |

