.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
House: townhouse, tower, gothic-revival, colonial, craftsman, farmhouse
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, march, february, june, april, may
1. the colonial house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is the townhouse house##1
5. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the farmhouse house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
7. the townhouse house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
8. the craftsman house is on the left of the tower house##1
9. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| House    | craftsman | tower | colonial | farmhouse    | townhouse | gothic-revival      |
| Birthday   | february   | october     | march      | april | may           | june |

