.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
6 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, bridge, scrabble, domino, poker
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, aristoff, davidoff, chaman, swisher, montecristo
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
7. the person playing poker is the alhambra-smoker##1
8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
9. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Game          | billiard | poker   | domino  | bridge    | scrabble  | monopoly |
| Cigar   | aristoff   | alhambra | montecristo | swisher | davidoff | chaman |

