.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, cottage, townhouse, colonial, craftsman
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, police-officer, manager, paramedic, project-manager, nurse
1. the police-officer is on the far left##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the project-manager is on the right of the colonial house##1
4. the paramedic is the townhouse house##1
5. the nurse is on the left of the manager##1
6. the craftsman house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
7. the cottage house is on the left of the coach##1
8. the police-officer is on the left of the craftsman house##1
9. the nurse is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| House   | colonial | craftsman | townhouse    | gothic-revival | cottage  | ranch-style |
| Job     | police-officer    | project-manager | paramedic | nurse   | manager | coach    |

