.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-13::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: black, coral, emerald, yellow, ebony, turquise
There are 6 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, fanta
1. the person who likes yellow is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes black is the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
7. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
9. the person who likes turquise is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Color         | emerald | coral | ebony | yellow | black    | turquise |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | lemonade      | hot-chocolate        | milk    | almond-milk | fanta  |

