3. the montecristo-smoker is the person eating strawberry##1
4. the chaman-smoker is the person eating plum##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
6. the person eating plum is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
8. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
| Food   | grapefruit | strawberry | plum  | cauliflower | kiwi       | spinach   |
| Cigar   | vegafina | montecristo     | chaman | pall-mall        | cain | alhambra |

