.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff, chaman, ritmeester, davidoff, cain
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, september, may, december, february, april
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Cigar   | aristoff | cain     | davidoff       | chaman  | ritmeester | tiparillo    |
| Birthday     | april  | november | september | december | february  | may |

 